UIGridView is a simple UI class that lays out views you provided in a grid like fashion.

Usage
-----
Interface is a delegate pattern where it requires a few simple methods to be implemented:

- (NSInteger)numberOfColumnsInGridView:(UIGridView *)gridView; // specifies number of columns desired
- (NSInteger)numberOfViewsInGridView:(UIGridView *)gridView; // specifies number of views you want to display
- (UIView *)gridView:(UIGridView *)gridView viewForIndex:(NSInteger)index; // return the view you'd like to display at a specific index

Unsupported
-----------
- Customizable view placement within grid blocks (center align, left align...etc.)
